> chances of success will be.  Using the "10" row and the "4d6" column, we see
> that the player has about a 16% chance of accomplishing the task (marked with
> *asterisks*). If the GM sets the difficulty level lower, say at 3d6, the
> player's chances will increase (in this case, to 50%).
